Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:34.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}過ぎるだけの時間じゃ付与する
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:43.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}刻まなくちゃ　ここに居ると心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:52.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}涙をのみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:54.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}不器用だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:58.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:04.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大空を見上げ何も言えず
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:12.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}胸が痛む訳考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:14.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:23.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君と僕の仲で何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:33.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}キメキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:39.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:34.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}给予了我所度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:43.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}必须在这里刻下心灵吼叫的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:52.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}强忍着泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:54.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:58.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}连梦想也与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:04.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}看着天空一句话也说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:12.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直思考着胸口的那股痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:14.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}追赶着清风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:23.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你与我之间发生了什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:33.50,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}向着那耀眼的太阳所照耀之处前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:39.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永远什么的 我才不知道呢
